# List of source files containing translatable strings.
# Paths are relative to the project root (the directory containing meson.build).
# Regenerate the audit with:
#   grep -rlE "_\(['\"]" src --include='*.py'        # python
#   grep -rlE "_\(['\"]|C_\(['\"]" data --include='*.blp'  # blueprint
# Blueprint (.blp) files are extracted directly: their _("...") / C_("ctx","...")
# syntax is C-like, so xgettext's C lexer (via the meson 'glib' preset) reads them.

# --- Desktop entry / AppStream metadata (translatable fields) ---
data/io.github.tylerreece.timbre.desktop.in
